-
-### F&R Needed flag
-
-The Overview writes `F&R Needed = Yes` when an in-scope row has one of these F&R statuses:
+Only these in-scope F&R statuses trigger `F&R Needed = Yes`:
 
 - `Pending`
-- `N/A` / `NA` / common N/A variants
-
-`Approved` alone does not make `F&R Needed = Yes`, because it is already approved.
-
-### Numeric F&R item count
+- `Approved`
 
-The numeric F&R count includes only these statuses:
+Only these in-scope F&R statuses increment the numeric F&R count:
 
 - `Pending`
 - `Approved`
 
-`N/A` / `NA` does not increment the F&R count.
+The following statuses do not trigger `F&R Needed = Yes` and do not increment the F&R count:
+
+- `N/A`
+- `NA`
+- `N.A.`
+- `Not Applicable`
+- Blank values
+
+## Practical examples
+
+| In-scope F&R statuses | F&R Needed | F&R count |
+|---|---:|---:|
+| `N/A`, `NA` | `No` | `0` |
+| `Pending` | `Yes` | `1` |
+| `Approved` | `Yes` | `1` |
+| `Pending`, `Approved`, `N/A` | `Yes` | `2` |
 
